sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant Frontend as React Frontend
    participant Backend as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as Supabase PostgreSQL
    participant Maps as Google Maps / Street View
    participant AI as Claude Runtime Agents

    Player->>Frontend: Logs in and starts a game
    Frontend->>Backend: Create or resume game
    Backend->>DB: Store game and round state
    Backend-->>Frontend: Return round location data
    Frontend->>Maps: Load Street View panorama
    Player->>Frontend: Explores panorama and places guess

    opt Player requests hint
        Frontend->>Backend: Request hint with current panorama view
        Backend->>Maps: Fetch Street View static image
        Backend->>AI: Ask Hint Agent for visual hints
        AI-->>Backend: Return progressive hints
        Backend-->>Frontend: Return next hint and score penalty
    end

    Player->>Frontend: Submits guess
    Frontend->>Backend: Submit round result
    Backend->>AI: Ask Opponent Agent for PvE guess if enabled
    Backend->>DB: Save score, guess, hints, and AI explanation
    Backend-->>Frontend: Return score and round feedback
    Frontend-->>Player: Show real location, distance, and results
